VALUES
(42, 8, 3, 23, 23, 18, 18, 'ministered unto him of their substance', 'Holiness and Service Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of using resources for divine purposes. Both passages emphasize the idea of serving the Lord through material means, whether through ministering or dedicating merchandise to God.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 4, 41, 4, 1, 9, 'much people were gathered together', 'Teaching by Parables', 'Both passages emphasize Jesus teaching a large crowd through parables. The mention of a ''great multitude'' in Mark parallels the gathering of people in Luke, highlighting the significance of his teaching method.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 4, 40, 13, 2, 9, 'much people were gathered together', 'Gathering of the Multitudes', 'Both passages emphasize the gathering of large crowds to hear Jesus speak. This connection highlights the significance of parables as a teaching method used in response to the multitude''s presence.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 58, 2, 1, 1, NULL, 'Sowing and Heeding the Word', 'This connection highlights the importance of attentiveness to the message, as the seed that fell by the way side represents the failure to heed what is sown. Both passages emphasize the need to actively engage with what we have received to prevent it from being lost.', 'theme', 0.37, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 59, 1, 23, 24, NULL, 'Connection of Hearing and Action', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of response to what is received. The sower''s seed represents the word, and the hearer must act on it rather than forget it.', 'theme', 0.356, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 41, 4, 15, 15, 'by the way side', 'Connection of Sowing and Reception', 'This connection highlights the imagery of sowing seed and the immediate response to it. Both passages emphasize the fate of the seed that falls ''by the way side'' and its vulnerability to being taken away.', 'parallel', 0.349, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 42, 8, 11, 12, 'sowed, some fell by the way side', 'Connection of Sowing and Hearing', 'This connection highlights the imagery of sowing seed and its reception. Both passages emphasize the fate of the seed, with the first describing its physical downfall and the second explaining the spiritual consequence of the word being taken away.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 1, 15, 11, 11, 'fowls of the air devoured it', 'Fowls and Seed Connection', 'Both passages emphasize the presence of fowls that disrupt the intended outcome. In Luke, the fowls devour the seed, while in Genesis, Abram drives the fowls away from the carcasses, highlighting a theme of protection against disruption.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 41, 4, 26, 29, 'sow his seed', 'Connection of Sowing and Growth', 'Both passages emphasize the process of sowing seed and the subsequent growth that occurs, illustrating the natural progression from planting to harvest. This connection highlights the theme of the kingdom of God as a dynamic process involving both human action and divine growth.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 5, 19, 119, 118, 118, 'trodden down', 'Trodden Down Imagery', 'This connection highlights the imagery of being ''trodden down'' in both passages. In Luke, the seed is trodden down, while in Psalms, those who err are also trodden down, suggesting a thematic parallel of judgment and consequence.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 42, 8, 13, 13, 'upon a rock', 'Connection of the Rock Imagery', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of ''rock'' as a metaphor for those who receive the word but lack depth. The first passage describes the seed on the rock withering due to lack of moisture, while the second explains that those on the rock have no root and fall away in temptation.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 58, 3, 7, 8, 'lacked moisture', 'Connection of Spiritual Hardness', 'This connection highlights the theme of spiritual receptivity. Both passages emphasize the consequences of a hardened heart, leading to a lack of growth or nourishment, as seen in the withering of the seed.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 41, 4, 5, 6, 'withered away, because it lacked moisture', 'Connection of Soil Types', 'Both passages emphasize the challenges of growth on poor soil. They describe how the plants wither due to lack of moisture or depth, highlighting the theme of inadequate conditions for growth.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 45, 2, 4, 5, 'lacked moisture', 'Connection of Spiritual Growth', 'This connection highlights the theme of spiritual growth and the consequences of a lack of nourishment. In Luke, the seed withers away due to a lack of moisture, paralleling Romans where an impenitent heart leads to spiritual decay and judgment.', 'theme', 0.321, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 24, 5, 3, 3, NULL, 'Connection of Hardness and Lack', 'Both passages emphasize the theme of hardness, with the seed on the rock withering due to lack of moisture, paralleling the people in Jeremiah who have made their faces harder than a rock and refuse correction. This connection highlights the consequences of spiritual barrenness and resistance to change.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 26, 36, 26, 26, 'upon a rock', 'Stony Heart vs. Rock', 'This connection highlights the theme of barrenness due to hardness. In Luke, the seed withers on the rock, paralleling Ezekiel''s mention of a ''stony heart'' that needs transformation.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 6, 30, 6, 12, 12, 'upon a rock', 'Connection of Rock Imagery', 'This connection highlights the imagery of ''rock'' in both passages, where the rock symbolizes unfruitfulness and barrenness. Both verses emphasize the consequences of lacking essential elements for growth and righteousness.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 24, 4, 3, 3, 'among thorns', 'Connection of Thorns in Scripture', 'Both passages emphasize the detrimental effect of thorns on growth. Luke describes how thorns choke the seed, while Jeremiah warns against sowing among thorns, indicating a similar theme of hindrance in spiritual cultivation.', 'theme', 0.32799999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 42, 8, 14, 14, NULL, 'Connection of Thorns and Choking', 'Both passages emphasize the imagery of thorns choking the growth of seeds. The source verse describes the thorns choking the seed, while the target passage explains how cares and pleasures of life choke those who hear the word.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 1, 3, 18, 18, 'thorns', 'Connection of Thorns in Scripture', 'This connection highlights the theme of thorns representing obstacles and challenges in life. In Luke, thorns choke the growth of seeds, while in Genesis, thorns are a consequence of the curse, symbolizing the difficulties humanity faces.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 40, 13, 7, 7, NULL, 'Connection of Thorns in Parables', 'Both passages emphasize the imagery of thorns choking the seeds. This connection highlights the shared theme of obstacles to growth in the parables.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 40, 13, 22, 22, 'thorns sprang up with it, and choked it', 'Connection of Thorns and Unfruitfulness', 'Both passages emphasize the impact of thorns on growth. The thorns in Luke choke the seed, while Matthew elaborates on how worldly cares and riches contribute to unfruitfulness.', 'theme', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 7, 41, 4, 7, 7, 'fell among thorns', 'Connection of Thorn Imagery', 'Both passages emphasize the thorns that choked the seed, illustrating the same concept of obstacles preventing growth. The similar phrasing reinforces the idea of unfruitfulness due to competing elements.', 'parallel', 0.314, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
