(42, 8, 8, 66, 2, 11, 11, NULL, 'Hearing and Overcoming', 'This connection highlights the importance of listening and responding to God''s message. Both passages emphasize the phrase ''He that hath an ear, let him hear,'' linking the act of hearing to spiritual fruitfulness and overcoming challenges.', 'keyword', 0.33499999999999996, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 8, 20, 1, 20, 23, 'He that hath ears to hear, let him hear', 'Call to Listen and Respond', 'This connection highlights the theme of heeding wisdom''s call. Both passages emphasize the importance of listening and responding to the voice of wisdom, as seen in the call to ''hear'' in Luke and the urgent plea to ''turn'' in Proverbs.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
(42, 8, 8, 20, 20, 12, 12, 'He that hath ears to hear', 'Connection of Hearing and Understanding', 'Both passages emphasize the importance of hearing. Luke 8:8 highlights the call to listen, while Proverbs 20:12 states that the Lord has made the hearing ear.', 'theme', 0.321, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
